三、教學目標 Objectives


在多元化的公民社會中，大學教育除了提升學生專業能力與社會競爭力之外，更應提升對社會不同層面的關懷能力。關懷能力係奠基於生命歷練與知識涵養，自發性地對某一領域、現象、族群或議題之投入精神與作為，而期許美好之生命價值與意義。本課程即以當代社會不同領域與專業之精英，以專題演講之方式，分享生涯中的特殊關懷及其內涵，以期啟發本校學生的關懷之情與認知能力。 


In a wide range of civil society, university education in addition to enhancing students' professional ability and social competence, the more should enhance the ability of the different levels of social care. Caring ability system founded on the experience and knowledge of life conservation, spontaneously to a particular area, into the phenomenon, ethnic or issues with a spirit, and hopes for a better value and significance of life. The course that is different areas of contemporary society and professional elite, with a keynote speech of the way, share career in special care and content, in order to inspire our students care of the situation and cognitive abilities. 


